Package: cqThemes
Title: Ces Quarto Themes - Custom Themes for Quarto and R Markdown Documents
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Cesaire", "Tobias", email = "cesaire@sheetsolved.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000"))
Description: Provides consistent formatting, themes, and styling functions for
    different document types created with R Markdown or Quarto. Includes custom
    themes for PDF reports, HTML documents, and revealjs presentations. Features
    coordinated color palettes, responsive layouts, and helper functions for table
    formatting with various backends including 'kableExtra' for PDF and 'DT' for
    HTML. Also provides integration with both 'ggplot2' and 'plotly' for static
    and interactive visualizations.
